Features currently supported in this BNF:
Module declaration

Export declaration

Multiple function clauses with guards

Pattern matching in function parameters (variables, literals, tuples, lists, cons, maps, records)

Erlang-style operators (+, -, *, /, unary + and -)

Function calls

Complex data types: tuples, lists, maps

Strings and atoms

If-Else expressions (with multiple guarded clauses)

Case expressions (pattern matching with multiple clauses)
